---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout>
	<section class="pt-48 pb-32 min-h-screen" style="background-color: #F5F0E8;">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-6">
			<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-center mb-4" style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;">가격 안내</h1>
			<p class="text-center text-gray-600 mb-20" style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;">모든 견적은 제품의 모델링 난이도와 작업 범위에 따라 상이하며 정확한 금액은 상담 후 확정됩니다.</p>

			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 max-w-sm lg:max-w-none mx-auto" style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;">
				<!-- Standard -->
				<div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-5 lg:p-8 flex flex-col justify-between transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:-translate-y-2">
					<h2 class="text-xl lg:text-2xl font-bold" style="color: #5A4D43;">Standard</h2>
					<ul class="text-sm lg:text-base space-y-2 lg:space-y-5 text-gray-700 font-medium my-4 lg:my-6">
						<li class="pl-4 -indent-4">• 배경 없는 제품 단독 이미지 (누끼컷)</li>
						<li class="pl-4 -indent-4">• 고해상도 결과물 제공</li>
						<li class="pl-4 -indent-4">• 상업적 활용 가능</li>
						<li class="pl-4 -indent-4">• 기본 수정 2회 포함</li>
					</ul>
					<p class="text-right font-bold" style="color: #5A4D43;"><span class="text-xl lg:text-2xl">₩</span><span class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl">44,000원~</span></p>
				</div>

				<!-- Deluxe -->
				<div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-5 lg:p-8 flex flex-col justify-between transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:-translate-y-2">
					<h2 class="text-xl lg:text-2xl font-bold" style="color: #5A4D43;">Deluxe</h2>
					<ul class="text-sm lg:text-base space-y-2 lg:space-y-5 text-gray-700 font-medium my-4 lg:my-6">
						<li class="pl-4 -indent-4">• 제품이 돋보이는 단색 배경 이미지</li>
						<li class="pl-4 -indent-4">• 고해상도 결과물 제공</li>
						<li class="pl-4 -indent-4">• 상업적 활용 가능</li>
						<li class="pl-4 -indent-4">• 기본 수정 2회 포함</li>
					</ul>
					<p class="text-right font-bold" style="color: #5A4D43;"><span class="text-xl lg:text-2xl">₩</span><span class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl">66,000원~</span></p>
				</div>

				<!-- Premium -->
				<div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-5 lg:p-8 flex flex-col justify-between transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:-translate-y-2">
					<h2 class="text-xl lg:text-2xl font-bold" style="color: #5A4D43;">Premium</h2>
					<ul class="text-sm lg:text-base space-y-2 lg:space-y-5 text-gray-700 font-medium my-4 lg:my-6">
						<li class="pl-4 -indent-4">• 오브제, 조명, 구도를 활용해 연출한 감각적인 이미지</li>
						<li class="pl-4 -indent-4">• 고해상도 결과물 제공</li>
						<li class="pl-4 -indent-4">• 상업적 활용 가능</li>
						<li class="pl-4 -indent-4">• 기본 수정 2회 포함</li>
					</ul>
					<p class="text-right font-bold" style="color: #5A4D43;"><span class="text-xl lg:text-2xl">₩</span><span class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl">99,000원~</span></p>
				</div>

				<!-- Exclusive -->
				<div class="rounded-lg shadow-lg p-5 lg:p-8 flex flex-col justify-between relative overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:-translate-y-2" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3A2F27 0%, #7A6B5F 50%, #3A2F27 100%);">
					<h2 class="text-xl lg:text-2xl font-bold text-white relative z-10">Exclusive</h2>
					<ul class="text-sm lg:text-base space-y-1.5 lg:space-y-3 text-white font-medium relative z-10 my-4 lg:my-6">
						<li class="pl-4 -indent-4">• 제품 분석 및 브랜딩 기획</li>
						<li class="pl-4 -indent-4">• 연출 방향 및 레퍼런스 제안</li>
						<li class="pl-4 -indent-4">• 누끼컷(3), 단색 배경컷(4), 연출컷(3) 총 10컷 구성</li>
						<li class="pl-4 -indent-4">• 고해상도 결과물 제공</li>
						<li class="pl-4 -indent-4">• 상업적 활용 가능</li>
						<li class="pl-4 -indent-4">• 기본 수정 2회 포함</li>
					</ul>
					<p class="text-right font-bold text-white relative z-10"><span class="text-xl lg:text-2xl">₩</span><span class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl">820,000원~</span></p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</MainLayout>
